{
  "stem": "1062.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They were the border police.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They were known as [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The [NON-ENGLISH] are very rude, very cruel people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And from time to time, they would come into the ghetto just because of brutality.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they would beat-- my mother's brother was beaten up once.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He was bleeding.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They just beat him up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "In the ghetto, there was nothing to eat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they told everybody-- we were in one room, like maybe in a little room, we were mashed, I mean, maybe 20 people, 25 people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "You know, hardly for people to lay down, one next to the other, and sleep.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they told us to dig outside the house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to dig for latrines, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Trenches.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a rabbi there who said that if Jewish man and woman get married, if boys and girls get married, this is [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] means it's a redemption.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's a mitzvah to get married.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember everybody was grabbing, and they were running and getting married.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the interesting part of this, the rich people would marry poor girls.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, because if you marry-- a rich man marries a poor girl, it's even more of a mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they tried to make mitzvahs over there, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because people, they believed in it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, this was a way of life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in the ghetto, you know, there were children there too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I remember certain instances there where the children, they didn't have a-- the children, see?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When you get up in the morning, we were taught to say the Modeh Ani.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have to recite a certain prayer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Every child was trained when you get up in the morning to recite the Modeh Ani before you could eat.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the children would cry for food.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
